9 AN ACT TO MAKE AN APPROPRIATION FOR EXPENSES FOR THE
10 ARKANSAS SENATE OF THE NINETY-FIFTH GENERAL ASSMEBLY
11 FOR THE FISCAL YEAR ENDING JUNE 30, 2025; AND FOR
12 OTHER PURPOSES.
