Subtitle
15
16 AN ACT FOR THE EXPENSES FOR THE ARKANSAS
17 SENATE OF THE NINETY-FIFTH GENERAL
18 ASSEMBLY APPROPRIATION FOR THE 2025
19 FISCAL YEAR.
20
21
22 BE IT ENACTED BY THE GENERAL ASSEMBLY OF THE STATE OF ARKANSAS:
23
24 SECTION 1. APPROPRIATION SENATE EXPENSES. There is hereby
25 appropriated, to the Arkansas Senate, to be payable from the Constitutional
26 Officers Fund, for the fiscal year ending June 30, 2025, the following:
27 (A) for Mileage Allowances, Per diem, Maintenance and General
28 Operations and other expenses authorized by law, the sum of ........$675,000.
29 (B) for Salaries of Employees, in a sum not to exceed ........$650,000.
30 (C) for Employer Matching Funds, in a sum not to exceed .......$75,000.
31
32 SECTION 2. SPECIAL LANGUAGE. NOT TO BE INCORPORATED INTO THE ARKANSAS
33 CODE NOR PUBLISHED SEPARATELY AS SPECIAL, LOCAL AND TEMPORARY LAW. TRANSFER.
34 If the Senate Efficiency Committee and the Secretary of the Senate, subject
35 to approval by the Arkansas Senate, should determine that any item or portion
36 thereof appropriated herein for a specific purpose is not needed for such
